Lesotho Annual Inflation Rate Rises to 4.1% in April, Statistics Body Says

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-05-25T06:59:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/lesotho-annual-inflation-rate-rises-to-4-1-in-april-statistics-body-says.html
Lesotho’s inflation rate rose to an
annual 4.1 percent in April, the nation’s statistics agency
said.  Inflation quickened 0.5 percentage point from March, the
Maseru-based National Statistics Office said in an e-mailed
statement today. Electricity, gas and other fuels climbed 16
percent, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  